# Reference credentials for the azure-proof example. Copy to '.baron/credentials'
# (gitignored) in your own project, or export these in your environment. Never commit real values.
# Azure DevOps powers issues + scm + ci + deploy (org/project/repo are coordinates, not secrets;
# only the token is secret). Slack powers notify.

AZURE_DEVOPS_ORG=
AZURE_DEVOPS_PROJECT=
AZURE_DEVOPS_REPO=
AZURE_DEVOPS_TOKEN=

SLACK_BOT_TOKEN=
SLACK_CHANNEL=
